column5: HI all,  I like to follow some of the viral vids on youtube. They are weird and funny and become the 'in' joke at work for a while until another one is discovered . At the moment the video we laugh about is a weird kid singing his own song...."Chocolate Rain".....   <iframe width="420" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/EwTZ2xpQwpA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>     I guess i sing it more often than i realise, and make a silly face while doing it...cuz my wife got Jack singing it on video for me last night .....sooooo funny....tooo cute...if not a little weird.   <iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/apgMIK30PZs" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
Choc-lit raaayyyyyyne  Now you got me singin' it
LOL...you might like 'Chad Vader's' version too.   <iframe width="420" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/P6dUCOS1bM0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
When is G-man hitting the water again? we are due a post dontchafink?
we're hopin' soon. East winds the last few weekends
